## Project Structure

```
SmartCampusAPI/
├── pom.xml
├── src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml
└── src/main/java/com/smartcampus/
    ├── SmartCampusApplication.java             ← @ApplicationPath("/api/v1") — Part 1
    ├── DataStore.java                          ← Singleton ConcurrentHashMap store
    ├── model/
    │   ├── Room.java                           ← Room POJO
    │   ├── Sensor.java                         ← Sensor POJO
    │   └── SensorReading.java                  ← SensorReading POJO (UUID auto-generated)
    ├── resource/
    │   ├── DiscoveryResource.java              ← GET /api/v1  (Part 1)
    │   ├── RoomResource.java                   ← GET,POST,DELETE /rooms  (Part 2)
    │   ├── SensorResource.java                 ← GET,POST /sensors + sub-resource locator (Part 3 & 4)
    │   └── SensorReadingResource.java          ← GET,POST /readings  (Part 4)
    ├── exception/
    │   ├── RoomNotEmptyException.java          ← Part 5.1
    │   ├── RoomNotEmptyExceptionMapper.java    ← 409 Conflict
    │   ├── LinkedResourceNotFoundException.java          ← Part 5.2
    │   ├── LinkedResourceNotFoundExceptionMapper.java    ← 422 Unprocessable Entity
    │   ├── SensorUnavailableException.java     ← Part 5.3
    │   ├── SensorUnavailableExceptionMapper.java         ← 403 Forbidden
    │   └── GlobalExceptionMapper.java          ← 500 catch-all (Part 5.4)
    └── filter/
        └── LoggingFilter.java                  ← Request + Response logging (Part 5.5)
```

